description:
This package is a wrapper of GDAL 3.9 native dlls. It's a foundational component for various ThinkGeo packages and should not be directly referenced in projects. 
		
GDAL is a translator library for raster and vector geospatial data formats released under an X/MIT style Open Source license by the Open Source Geospatial Foundation. 

Supported Platforms: Linux X64
title: ThinkGeo Gdal Dependency for Linux
